condition.narrative: Finance Agreement :Maintenance of Steering Committee and PCU | Description :The Recipient shall maintain throughout the period ofProject implementation: (i) the Steering Committee to serve as the oversight entity for the Project; and (ii) the ProjectCoordination Unit within MCMEJF to run the day-to-day management of the Project; both with the composition and powers acceptable tothe Association as further described in the Project Operations Manual. | Frequency :CONTINUOUS

Finance Agreement :Signing of Partnership Contracts | Description :The Recipient shall make part of the proceeds of the Financingavailable under partnership contracts between the PCU and FODEFCA (for Comp. 1) and ANPE for (Comp. 2 and 3) as described in thePIM. The Recipient shall exercise its rights under each Partnership Contract in such manner as to protect the interests of theRecipient and the Association and to accomplish the purposes of the Financing. | Due Date :30-Sep-2014
